  "recommended_action": "Apply a targeted short-term redistribution of existing inventory from low-demand stores to replenish sizes 10-12 in affected mountain stores, supplemented by a modest emergency e-commerce fulfillment buffer for size 10-12 only. Do not initiate a new vendor order given the 6-week lead time; instead hold safety stock elsewhere and prioritize transfers and online fulfillment until the vendor cut arrives.",
